title: Argentina Domestic Car Sales
description: Car Registrations in Argentina decreased to 33.09 Thousand in October from 34.61 Thousand in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Argentina averaged 41.77 Thousand from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 90.31 Thousand in December of 2017 and a record low of 4 Thousand in January of 2002. This page provides - Argentina Domestic Car Sales - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Asociación de Fábricas de Automotores (ADEFA)
